public class MetadataContainer
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.VerticalPanel
implements CategoryAndTypeListener

The main purpose of these class is to be the manager of all the metadata of the medias, this widget has to be used (and reused) in the insert/edit mode of visualization for every media (images, videos, audios)
